		{
			question: "How much does it cost to finish a basement in Utah?",
			answer: "Most basement finishing projects in Utah County range from $40,000 to $80,000, depending on square footage, layout complexity, and finish level. A basic 1,000 sq ft basement with one bedroom and bathroom typically starts around $50,000–$60,000. High-end finishes, home theaters, wet bars, and multiple bathrooms will push costs higher. We provide transparent, detailed estimates so you know exactly where your money is going."
